OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,FA 23-year-old TikTok influencer
OL,8,Fcharged with the murder of her
OL,9,Fboyfriend in Dubai faces being
OL,10,Fexecuted by firing squad, a campaign
OL,11,Fgroup has said.
OL,13,FDetained in Dubai said it was
OL,14,Fassisting Brooke George, from
OL,15,FGravesend, Kent, who alleges she
OL,16,Fstabbed her 26-year-old British
OL,17,Fpartner in self-defence after she was
OL,18,F"repeatedly punched" and "feared for
OL,19,Fher life".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@TO]zD@ZOU{D@IO]
