PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,FGeorge met her partner online and
OL,8,Ftravelled to Dubai in the United Arab
OL,9,FEmirates (UAE) after developing a
OL,10,Frelationship with him, the campaign
OL,11,Fgroup said.
OL,13,FIt added that after a positive first
OL,14,Fvisit, George alleged her partner
OL,15,Fbecame "increasingly controlling and
OL,16,Fabusive" during a second trip.
OL,18,FAfter an evening at a bar in Dubai,
OL,19,FGeorge alleged her partner became
OL,20,Fintoxicated and assaulted her.
OL,26,@wD@HOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,FAccording to her family, George
OL,8,Fcontacted them in a state of panic
OL,9,Fafter being "repeatedly punched" and
OL,10,Fhad arranged a flight home before
OL,11,Freturning to the apartment to recover
OL,12,Fher passport, Detained in Dubai said.
OL,14,FThe group said her family alleged she
OL,15,Fwas "crying and begging for her
OL,16,Fpassport's return when she was punched
OL,17,Fhard in the face and attacked",
OL,18,Fadding: "Brooke says she feared for
OL,19,Fher life and, reaching for a kitchen
OL,20,Fknife within her grasp, acted in self-
OL,21,Fdefence."
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@`O]wD@EOUyD@^O]zD@IOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
