OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,FDetained in Dubai said she was
OL,8,Farrested in the early hours of Monday
OL,9,Fand charged with murder.
OL,11,FDetained in Dubai said George has
OL,12,Freceived "little explanation of the
OL,13,Fproceedings due to the language
OL,14,Fbarrier", as well as being "deprived
OL,15,Fof access to her embassy and forced to
OL,16,Fmake statements in the absence of a
OL,17,Flawyer".
OL,19,FThe influencer's mother, Thereza
OL,20,FGeorge, said she was "deeply concerned
OL,21,Ffor her welfare".
OL,26,@tD@JOUvD@HO]vD@\OUyD@GO]|D@VOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
