PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,FIn a statement, released through
OL,8,FDetained in Dubai, she said: "After
OL,9,FBrooke returned to Dubai for the
OL,10,Fsecond time, the dynamic between them
OL,11,Fhad clearly changed.
OL,13,F"The day before the incident, she did
OL,14,Fnot seem like herself. She was quieter
OL,15,Fand not her usual happy, cheerful
OL,16,Fself, but she did not tell me why.
OL,17,FThat evening they went to a bar in
OL,18,FDubai.
OL,26,@pD@^OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,F"When I spoke to Brooke right after
OL,8,Fthe incident, she was absolutely
OL,9,Fterrified. I have never seen my
OL,10,Fdaughter so frightened in my life. She
OL,11,Fwas crying uncontrollably. I could see
OL,12,Fthat one of her eyes was badly swollen
OL,13,Fand was beginning to close.
OL,15,F"The daughter I spoke to that night
OL,16,Fwas utterly terrified. I firmly
OL,17,Fbelieve she was desperately trying to
OL,18,Fget home and away from whatever had
OL,19,Fhappened to her."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
