PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,FRadha Stirling, chief executive of
OL,8,FDetained in Dubai, said that "rather
OL,9,Fthan treating Brooke solely as a
OL,10,Fmurder suspect, investigators must
OL,11,Falso examine her being the victim of
OL,12,Fserious violence and possible
OL,13,Fexploitation".
OL,15,FMs Stirling added: "We will be working
OL,16,Fto ensure that her rights are
OL,17,Fprotected, that she receives a fair
OL,18,Ftrial, and that the circumstances
OL,19,Fleading to this tragedy are fully and
OL,20,Fimpartially examined.
OL,26,@pD@^OUuD@MO]wD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782461893
OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,F"Those closest to Brooke became
OL,8,Fincreasingly concerned that she may
OL,9,Fhave been lured to Dubai under false
OL,10,Fpretences for the purpose of
OL,11,Fexploitation.
OL,13,F"Their concerns were fuelled by his
OL,14,Funexplained change in behaviour, the
OL,15,Fone way ticket, the bikini clad
OL,16,Fprofessional photo shoot arranged
OL,17,Fduring her first visit, the alleged
OL,18,Fwithholding of her passport, Brooke
OL,19,Ftelling friends that 'things weren't
OL,20,Fright', and her growing fear that she
OL,21,Fneeded to escape.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
