OL,3,CTikTok influencer charged with
OL,4,Cboyfriend's murder in Dubai 'faces
OL,5,Cfiring squad'
OL,7,FA Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,8,FDevelopment Office spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"We are in touch with a British woman
OL,10,Fdetained in the UAE, we are supporting
OL,11,Fher family, and we are in contact with
OL,12,Fthe local authorities."
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@WO]
